# ----------------------------------------------------
#  Game Messages:
#	A. Referee to Player Messages
#		1. Invalid Board Setup
#		2. Invalid Board Move <moveErrorType>
#		3. <position 1> <position 2> <player> <movetype>
#		4. F <position>
# 		5. <winningPlayer> Victory
#	B. Player to Referee Messages
